Start Your Xammp and Activate Apache and Mysqlserver
#Step-1:

$ pip install pymysql

open the init.py file of the main app and add->


import pymysql
pymysql.version_info = (1, 3, 13, "final", 0)
pymysql.install_as_MySQLdb()


#Step-2:

If it throws a error like "Visual c++ 14 is required" then go to -> https://www.scivision.dev/python-windows-visual-c-14-required/


#Step-3: mysqlclient can be installed through the manual way. Go to -> https://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/

Download appropriate version of mysqlclient based on your python version.

Then $pip install mysqlclient...whl
